.: Plot :.
A comedy centered around six 30-something friends who each think the other has it better.
The series follows the lives of six friends, all of whom are at different stages of their lives and thinking that each other has it better. Will (James Van Der Beek) is a newly-single bachelor pining for his ex-wife; Jules (Brooklyn Decker) and Lowell (Rick Donald) are newly engaged; Kate (Zoe Lister-Jones) is a successful career woman who does not have the best luck with dating; and Andi (Majandra Delfino) and Bobby (Kevin Connolly) are a happily married couple pining for their younger fun days.[/b]
